Linux
=====

Run the following commands to install

    $ cd src/
    $ qmake
    $ make
    $ ewhereinblog-desktop-notifier ../linux/
    $ linux
    $ h install.sh

Windows
=======

Open somewhereinblog-desktop-notifier.pro with Qt Creator or run qmake.
Put the output exe with the following DLLs.

libgcc_s_dw2-1.dll
QtCore4.dll
QtXml4.dll
QtGui4.dll
mingwm10.dll
QtNetwork4.dll
